It's a stereo,

17:33.000 --> 17:35.000
and it plays music from the Internet.

17:35.000 --> 17:37.000
It comes through these speakers.

17:40.000 --> 17:41.000
Pretty good, huh?

17:42.000 --> 17:43.000
It's a good song.

17:43.000 --> 17:45.000
Here, check it, check it, check it.

