Yeah, check it out.

18:46.000 --> 18:47.000
Twinsies.

18:47.000 --> 18:50.000
Hey, nice clothes. Is that vintage?

18:51.000 --> 18:52.000
-Good, huh? -Hmm?

18:52.000 --> 18:54.000
Kosher, too.

