19:02.000 --> 19:05.000
How many pairs of shoes you own?

19:05.000 --> 19:07.000
Um, like seven, maybe?

19:07.000 --> 19:11.000
Seven. How many sock?

19:11.000 --> 19:13.000
I have like 20, 25 pairs of socks.

19:13.000 --> 19:14.000
[chuckles]

19:15.000 --> 19:18.000
Twenty-five socks! Twenty-five.

19:18.000 --> 19:19.000
It's a lot of socks.

19:19.000 --> 19:21.000
-You only have two feet, right? -[laughs]

19:21.000 --> 19:24.000
No, it's just these. [laughs]

19:25.000 --> 19:30.000
Ben Greenbaum. Owner of 25 pair of sock.

19:30.000 --> 19:31.000
It's pretty normal for today.

19:31.000 --> 19:33.000
Tell me, what is it you do for job?

19:33.000 --> 19:35.000
Wait, let me guess. You're a doctor.

19:35.000 --> 19:38.000
No. You're a lawyer.

19:38.000 --> 19:39.000
No.

