Close. Freelance mobile app developer.

19:42.000 --> 19:43.000
What?

19:44.000 --> 19:46.000
It's easier if I show you.

19:46.000 --> 19:47.000
Here, come on.

19:47.000 --> 19:51.000
You're gonna think it's dope. Which means "good."

19:51.000 --> 19:53.000
Check it out, man.

19:53.000 --> 19:54.000
Go.

