Also, they want to know

20:15.000 --> 20:18.000
whether or not the company they're buying from is ethical.

20:18.000 --> 20:19.000
-They do? -Yes.

20:19.000 --> 20:21.000
They do. It's called "conscientious shopping."

20:19.000 --> 20:21.000
It's very popular.

20:22.000 --> 20:23.000
My app makes it very easy.

20:23.000 --> 20:25.000
All you do is, you scan a product.

20:25.000 --> 20:27.000
