Thanks to Boop Bop.

20:50.000 --> 20:51.000
-"Boop Bop"? -Boop Bop, yeah.

20:52.000 --> 20:53.000
-It's called "Boop Bop." -Why Boop Bop?

20:54.000 --> 20:55.000
Um...

